  m_text: "Hello, \n\nthis file serves as a guide to help you work with file viewer.\n\nIn
    this application you can:\n\t- Move the file using your mouse.\n\t- Zoom in and
    out using the buttons above, \n\t  or using the scroll wheel on your mouse\n\t-
    Some text is also interactable. <u><link=\"ChangeColor\"><color=Black>Try clicking
    me</color></link></u>"
